{"tid":101190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"怪客紋身用古文問價 紋身師傅妙問妙答","createTime":"2017-01-30T15:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T16:52:18.000Z","uid":75927,"like":12,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aea6dccae667b321d6d5ec74bee3cd97c5023b1a","tid":101190,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"現在不少店鋪都喜歡在網上開設 Facebook 專頁、網站等等，可能隔著網站，所以經常會遇到一些奇怪的客人。近日有一位紋身師傅在 Facebook 專頁放出相片，指「第一次遇到有人咁樣問紋身！」究竟這位客人有多特別令師傅特地截圖放上來分享？<br />\n<br />\n原來，這位客人就用 WhatsApp 詢問紋身相關的資料，但全段文字卻是文言文，内容大概是見到一種「如蝠似魚」的大型魚類，想把牠紋在身上。想不到紋身師傅都妙問妙答，竟然同樣以文言文回答。並反問客人想將「海蝠」紋在身體何處、紋身大小以及客人想要的畫風。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都認爲，紋身師傅好厲害，實在「有文彩」、大讚師傅是「神回覆，佩服！」，還立刻讚了專頁。更加有不少網民同樣用文言文留言，說「汝之文彩，有幸見之，其樂也」、「吾欲知後事如何」。不過，都有網民認爲師傅最後差了一點，那句「等緊汝應機也」破壞了整段文字。不知道大家有沒有遇過喜歡用古文對答的朋友？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/rTLDwAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FrTLDwAL.jpg&h=a184fa6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:尹鬆<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=22112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fchannelnews.php%3Fid%3D22112&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=99d3a5ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=22112</a><br />\n<br />\n原Post:Takey Tattoo 臉書 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1704417519794844/photos/a.1777268772509718.1073741834.1704417519794844/1997032120533381/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1704417519794844%2Fphotos%2Fa.1777268772509718.1073741834.1704417519794844%2F1997032120533381%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2dad3003\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1704417519794844/photos/a.1777268772509718.1073741834.1704417519794844/1997032120533381/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n埃兹:Takeytattoo<br />\n<br />\n顧客Facebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kayan.the?lst=100003721939760%3A100003625080991%3A1485790206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkayan.the%3Flst%3D100003721939760%253A100003625080991%253A1485790206&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a163b358\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kayan.the?lst=100003721939760%3A100003625080991%3A1485790206</a><br />\n<br />\n顧客埃兹:木有"},{"pid":"c4ec2e7041ad6a092d698e637278c10eb758d430","tid":101190,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"好過好多扮識寫文言文既人"},{"pid":"fc33063fe425e106f9e28fe6c6c3a153f5089094","tid":101190,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"等緊汝應機也<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af68d50b5633929b0dc55b30ec27f0f185eca75","tid":101190,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"有無人可以解比我聽<br />\n岩岩係英國學完a-z排序返黎"},{"pid":"a48270629ba42e3029e3b9f26f0cccb43e4b82d1","tid":101190,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:47:10.000Z","msg":"UP"},{"pid":"637de0f1809098899c2f1e49f335d5d8398e29ad","tid":101190,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"f5e9e5d5c6ab5126f20f71010a19bbf38d494d32","tid":101190,"uid":75927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"0ba48c38658c4e689eab1702f63002c6dea426f4","tid":101190,"uid":42878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"好似幾大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ff41d6490127cc5f4d36aa48b27432df44e8c9","tid":101190,"uid":2440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等緊汝應機也<img